The paper discusses the quality of scientific entries in Wikipedia, specifically in the field of science. The analysis focuses on the outbound links from Wikipedia articles to scientific journals, which suggests that the paper is related to digital libraries (cs.DL), information retrieval (cs.IR), computational linguistics (cs.CL), cybernetics (cs.CY), and social and information networks (cs.SI).
